    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Some might say that you should go out and live a little, but they clearly haven't read a good book.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You often find yourself in a situation similar to something you read in a book. Your Intelligence Score maximum is increased by 2 and twice per short rest you can add a d6 to any d20 roll. You also have advantage on finding information from a book.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>You might have cut some gym time from your schedule to read more. You suffer a minus 1 to Strength and Dexterity saves and ability checks.</p><p></p>",
